If you have been playing around with network aesthetics, you have probably spend some time trying to figure out what layout works best to represent your data. After all, network's sole purpose is to visually represent _many complex_ relationships in a meaningful and digestable way. This step should not be underestimated! Thankfully, igraph has several [layouts](https://r-graph-gallery.com/247-network-chart-layouts.html) you can use. 

